				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="infobox biography vcard" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size:125%; font-weight:bold;"><span class="fn">Hendrik Pieter Nicolaas Muller</span></th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:M_VA0958.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1c/M_VA0958.jpg/225px-M_VA0958.jpg" width="225" height="319" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1c/M_VA0958.jpg/338px-M_VA0958.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1c/M_VA0958.jpg/450px-M_VA0958.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
<span style="">Dr. Hendrik P.N. Muller</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
